   version stable 0.2.8 0.2.7 0.2.6
  category utility
 attribute console
    source http://users.softlab.ece.ntua.gr/~thkala/projects/actkbd/files/actkbd-$VERSION.tar.bz2
      info good 20120531
      info last 20090130
      info home http://users.softlab.ece.ntua.gr/~thkala/projects/actkbd/actkbd.html
      info docs http://users.softlab.ece.ntua.gr/~thkala/projects/actkbd/latest/README
      desc 'daemon that binds actions to keyboard events
It recognises key combinations and can handle press,
repeat and release events.
Currently it only supports the linux-2.6 evdev interface,
but the platform-specific code is well-contained,
so that support for additional platforms can be added
with no or minimal changes to the rest of the code.'

build(){
sed -i "s:-O2 -Wall:$CFLAGS:" Makefile
make &&
make install prefix=$DESTDIR/usr
}
